<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >HR Service Continuity</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="e272a492-f9fe-4253-b400-d71559a6993f" >

    <p>Ryerson Human Resources has been working diligently to ensure that HR services are available to leaders and employees. In some cases, there may be changes to how you access them.</p> 
<h2>General HR support</h2> 
<p>Please note that the general 416-979-5075 will not be in service during this period.</p> 
<p>Support for general HR inquiries, job application and pay continues to be available through <a href="mailto:hr@ryerson.ca">hr@ryerson.ca</a>.</p>
    





</div>
