<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="ed84b6fd-f239-4405-8e7a-4013fb774459" >

    <p>As a reminder, employees and leaders who submit timesheets should continue to follow the standard process and <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/hr/manager-resources/pay-schedules-deadlines/">payroll deadlines</a>. Review <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/covid-19/updates/2020/03/pay-continuity-and-sick-leave-processes-during-covid-19-for-employees-who-submit-timesheets/">more information about submitting your timesheets during this period online</a>.</p> 
<p><strong>To ensure pay continuity, we strongly encourage any employees who receive paper cheques to sign up for direct deposit as soon as possible. Visit the <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/hr/learning-workshops/how-to-eHR/payroll/">eHR tutorial on payroll for instructions.</a></strong></p>
    





