                        <a id="accordion-1585152738767-pension-and-benefit-administration" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1585152738767-pension-and-benefit-administration" aria-controls="accordion-content-1585152738767-pension-and-benefit-administration" aria-expanded="false">
                            Pension and benefit administration
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1585152738767-pension-and-benefit-administration" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1585152738767-pension-and-benefit-administration">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1585152738767 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="524a706e-9539-4e1c-8364-29d3a6022957" >

    <p><a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/hr/contact/pension-benefits/">Pension and benefit administration</a> continues during this period.</p> 
<p>If you are working through the process of buying back pensionable service, please note that there may be a delay in depositing your cheques.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>Please also note that Sun Life has advised Ryerson of an increase of claim submissions, so there may be a delay in claim processing and reimbursement.&nbsp;</p> 
<h3>Out-of-province and out-of-country coverage&nbsp;</h3> 
<p>Employees with benefits who have out-of-province/out-of-country travel coverage should note:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>There are no extensions to the 180 day coverage limit.&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>Sun Life cannot guarantee the level of healthcare available depending on where you travel.&nbsp;</li> 
</ul> 
<p>Please be reminded that:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>all university-sanctioned international travel by students and staff is cancelled until August 31 or further notice; and,</li> 
 <li>all university-sanctioned international travel by faculty is to be avoided until August 31 or further notice.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>We also strongly urge anyone planning to travel to review the <a href="https://travel.gc.ca/travelling/advisories">Government of Canada’s current travel advisory<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>.</p>
    





</div>
