<p>Contracts that are expiring before the end of the semester that would have continued were it not for COVID-19, should be extended until the end of the semester.&nbsp;</p> 
<p><strong>If you were not planning to extend the term contract</strong> because the work is no longer available or because of performance issues, please <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/hr/contact/consulting-services/">connect with your HR partner</a> for further discussion.</p> 
<p>While the university is operating in an essential services model, OPSEU has agreed to extend any short-term temporary (STT) assignments which are scheduled to end by April 30 for up to three months.</p>
    





